Message: A profile deletion triggered the Windows All-User Install Agent to uninstall all packages for the user profile {Param1}.

The Windows All-User Install Agent will delete {NumberOfPackages} packages for user SID {UserSid} because the profile was deleted.
The Windows All-User Install Agent could not retrieve a list of packages for user SID {UserSid}. The error code is {Error}.
The Windows All-User Install Agent will delete package {Package} for user SID {UserSid} because the profile was deleted.
